content.body:
### Shop 25x12.00 - 9 Tire Size
In the power sports community, 25x12.00 - 9 is a popular tire size for ATVs, UTVs and quads. If you’ve got an ATV and are looking for tires in the 25x12.00 - 9 size, SimpleTire has plenty of options for you. 

Check out tires like the tough Interco Swamp Lite, Deestone Swamp Witch D932, Deestone D929 or the Greenball Dirt Devil A/T, which features an innovative ag-style angled lug tread for traction in sand and loose dirt. Other great options include the [Carlisle Knobby](https://simpletire.com/brands/carlisle-tires/knobby), with its more traditional knob tread design, and the Carlisle Turf Trac R/S, which is suitable for light-duty ATV use or for lawn/turf equipment. 

Whether you drive an ATV, UTV, mower, or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 25x12.00 - 9 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
